quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  6,74,"[Janto] tuma nde Ibraa hiima maakannoo ben makko Aazara: \"Ea jogitoto sanamuuji reweteeɗi?\" Pellet, min miɗo yi'e an e yimɓe maa ɓen,e nder majjere ɓanngunde"
  6,75,"Ko wano non Men holliri Ibraahiima laamuuji kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin, e fii yo o jeye e yananaaɓe ɓen"
  6,76,"Nde jemma on niɓɓitunoo e makko, o tini hoodere, o maaki : \"Ndee ɗoo ko joomi am!\" Ɓaawo nde mutii, o maaki : \"Mi yiɗaa mutooɓe ɓen"
  6,77,"Nde o tini lewru ndun no jalbi, o maaki : \"Nduu ɗoo ko joomi am!\" Ɓaawo ndu mutii, o maaki : \"Si Joomi am fewnaali lam, ma mi jeye e yimɓe majjuɓe ɓen"
  6,78,"Nde o tinunoo naange ngen no jalbi, o maaki : \"Ngee ɗoo ko joomi am! Ko ngee ɗoo ɓuri mawnude\" Ɓaawo nge mutii, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimɓe am, min ko mi daɗndiiɗo e kon ko sirkoton"
  6,79,"Min dey mi fewtinirii yeeso am ngon e On Taguɗo kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin ; ooñiiɗo=haniifiyanke, min mi jeyaaka e sirkooɓe ɓen"
  6,80,"Yimɓe makko ɓen wennji mo ; o maaki : \"E on wennjay lam fii Alla, gomɗii le O fewnii lam? Mi hulataa kon ko kafidoton e Makko, si wanaa nde Joomi am Muuyi huunde. Joomi am yaajanii kala huunde anndal. E on waajitotaako"
  6,81,Ko honno mi hulirta kon ko kafiduɗon on hulaali onon le on kafidii Alla e huunde nde O Jippinanaali on hujja? Ko honnde e feddeeji ɗin ɗiɗi ɓuri hanndude e deeƴere? Si on laatike annduɓe